					<description><![CDATA[ग्लोबल ब्रांड्स मैगज़ीन द्वारा आयोजित ग्लोबल ब्रांड अवार्ड्स 2025 में &#8220;बेस्ट फॉरेक्स MT4 ब्रोकर &#8211; एशिया 2025&#8243; अवार्ड जीतकर ATFX ने अपनी इंडस्‍ट्री लीडरशिप एक बार फिर प्रमाणित की। एशियाई बाज़ार में अपनी मजबूत मौजूदगी पुख्ता करते हुए ट्रेडिंग प्लेटफ़ॉर्म से सहज ट्रेडिंग अनुभव उपलब्‍ध करवाने में यह प्रतिष्ठित मान्यता ATFX की निरंतर उत्कृष्टता उजागर [&#8230;]]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span data-contrast="auto">ग्लोबल</span> <span data-contrast="auto">ब्रांड्स</span> <span data-contrast="auto">मैगज़ीन</span> <span data-contrast="auto">द्वारा</span> <span data-contrast="auto">आयोजित</span> <span data-contrast="auto">ग्लोबल</span> <span data-contrast="auto">ब्रांड</span> <span data-contrast="auto">अवार्ड्स</span> <span data-contrast="auto">2025</span> <span data-contrast="auto">में</span><span data-contrast="auto"> &#8220;</span><span data-contrast="auto">बेस्ट</span> <span data-contrast="auto">फॉरेक्स</span> <a href="https://www.atfx.com/hi-in/trading-platforms/metatrader-4" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i><span data-contrast="none">MT4</span></i></a> <span data-contrast="auto">ब्रोकर</span><span data-contrast="auto"> &#8211; </span><span data-contrast="auto">एशिया</span> <span data-contrast="auto">2025&#8243; </span><span data-contrast="auto">अवार्ड</span> <span data-contrast="auto">जीतकर</span> <span data-contrast="auto">ATFX </span><span data-contrast="auto">ने</span> <span data-contrast="auto">अपनी</span> <span data-contrast="auto">इंडस्</span><span data-contrast="auto">&#x200d;</span><span data-contrast="auto">ट्री</span> <span data-contrast="auto">लीडरशिप</span> <span data-contrast="auto">एक</span> <span data-contrast="auto">बार</span> <span data-contrast="auto">फिर</span> <span data-contrast="auto">प्रमाणित</span> <span data-contrast="auto">की।</span> <span data-contrast="auto">एशियाई</span> <span data-contrast="auto">बाज़ार</span> <span data-contrast="auto">में</span> <span data-contrast="auto">अपनी</span> <span data-contrast="auto">मजबूत</span> <span data-contrast="auto">मौजूदगी</span> <span data-contrast="auto">पुख्ता</span> <span data-contrast="auto">करते</span> <span data-contrast="auto">हुए</span> <span data-contrast="auto">ट्रेडिंग</span> <span data-contrast="auto">प्लेटफ़ॉर्म</span> <span data-contrast="auto">से</span> <span data-contrast="auto">सहज</span> <span data-contrast="auto">ट्रेडिंग</span> <span data-contrast="auto">अनुभव</span> <span data-contrast="auto">उपलब्</span><span data-contrast="auto">&#x200d;</span><span data-contrast="auto">ध</span> <span data-contrast="auto">करवाने</span> <span data-contrast="auto">में</span> <span data-contrast="auto">यह</span> <span data-contrast="auto">प्रतिष्ठित</span> <span data-contrast="auto">मान्यता</span> <span data-contrast="auto">ATFX </span><span data-contrast="auto">की</span> <span data-contrast="auto">निरंतर</span> <span data-contrast="auto">उत्कृष्टता</span> <span data-contrast="auto">उजागर</span> <span data-contrast="auto">करती</span> <span data-contrast="auto">है।</span></p>
<p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-47119" src="https://www.atfx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Announcement_20250320_Global-Brand-Awards_a_EN.webp" alt="Announcement_20250320_Global Brand Awards_a_EN" width="877" height="493" srcset="https://www.atfx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Announcement_20250320_Global-Brand-Awards_a_EN.webp 2560w, https://www.atfx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Announcement_20250320_Global-Brand-Awards_a_EN-300x169.webp 300w, https://www.atfx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Announcement_20250320_Global-Brand-Awards_a_EN-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://www.atfx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Announcement_20250320_Global-Brand-Awards_a_EN-768x432.webp 768w, https://www.atfx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Announcement_20250320_Global-Brand-Awards_a_EN-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://www.atfx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Announcement_20250320_Global-Brand-Awards_a_EN-2048x1152.webp 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 877px) 100vw, 877px" /></p>
<p><span data-contrast="auto">यह</span> <span data-contrast="auto">अवार्ड</span> <span data-contrast="auto">नवाचार</span><span data-contrast="auto">, </span><span data-contrast="auto">अत्याधुनिक</span> <span data-contrast="auto">तकनीक</span> <span data-contrast="auto">और</span> <span data-contrast="auto">बेहतर</span> <span data-contrast="auto">कस्</span><span data-contrast="auto">&#x200d;</span><span data-contrast="auto">टमर</span> <span data-contrast="auto">सर्विस</span> <span data-contrast="auto">के</span> <span data-contrast="auto">प्रति</span> <span data-contrast="auto">ATFX </span><span data-contrast="auto">की</span> <span data-contrast="auto">प्रतिबद्धता</span> <span data-contrast="auto">उजागर</span> <span data-contrast="auto">करता</span> <span data-contrast="auto">है।</span> <span data-contrast="auto">उन्नत</span> <span data-contrast="auto">ट्रेडिंग</span> <span data-contrast="auto">टूल</span><span data-contrast="auto">, </span><span data-contrast="auto">प्रतिस्पर्धी</span> <span data-contrast="auto">स्प्रेड</span> <span data-contrast="auto">और</span> <span data-contrast="auto">बिजली</span> <span data-contrast="auto">जैसी</span> <span data-contrast="auto">तेज</span> <span data-contrast="auto">गति</span> <span data-contrast="auto">के</span> <span data-contrast="auto">निष्पादन</span> <span data-contrast="auto">से</span> <span data-contrast="auto">कंपनी</span> <span data-contrast="auto">ने</span> <span data-contrast="auto">अपना</span> <span data-contrast="auto">ट्रेडिंग</span> <span data-contrast="auto">प्लेटफ़ॉर्म</span> <span data-contrast="auto">लगातार</span> <span data-contrast="auto">बेहतर</span> <span data-contrast="auto">बनाया</span> <span data-contrast="auto">है</span><span data-contrast="auto">, </span><span data-contrast="auto">जिससे</span> <span data-contrast="auto">ट्रेडरों</span> <span data-contrast="auto">को</span> <span data-contrast="auto">सर्वोत्तम</span> <span data-contrast="auto">संभव</span> <span data-contrast="auto">ट्रेडिंग</span> <span dat