<p><span data-contrast="auto">ट्रेडरों</span> <span data-contrast="auto">की</span> <span data-contrast="auto">उभरती</span> <span data-contrast="auto">ज़रूरतें</span> <span data-contrast="auto">पूरी</span> <span data-contrast="auto">करने</span> <span data-contrast="auto">के</span> <span data-contrast="auto">लिए</span> <span data-contrast="auto">पिछले</span> <span data-contrast="auto">कुछ</span> <span data-contrast="auto">वर्षों</span> <span data-contrast="auto">में</span><span data-contrast="auto">, ATFX </span><span data-contrast="auto">ने</span> <span data-contrast="auto">अपनी</span> <span data-contrast="auto">सर्विसेस</span> <span data-contrast="auto">फैलाकर</span><span data-contrast="auto">, </span><span data-contrast="auto">शैक्षिक</span> <span data-contrast="auto">संसाधन</span><span data-contrast="auto">, </span><span data-contrast="auto">व्यक्तिगत</span> <span data-contrast="auto">कस्</span><span data-contrast="auto">&#x200d;</span><span data-contrast="auto">टमर</span> <span data-contrast="auto">सपोर्ट</span> <span data-contrast="auto">और</span> <span data-contrast="auto">सुरक्षित</span> <span data-contrast="auto">ट्रेडिंग</span> <span data-contrast="auto">इंफ्रास्ट्रक्चर</span> <span data-contrast="auto">ऑफर</span> <span data-contrast="auto">किया</span> <span data-contrast="auto">है।</span> <span data-contrast="auto">ट्रेडर</span> <span data-contrast="auto">आसानी</span> <span data-contrast="auto">से</span> <span data-contrast="auto">ट्रेड</span> <span data-contrast="auto">करें</span><span data-contrast="auto">, </span><span data-contrast="auto">इसके</span> <span data-contrast="auto">लिए</span> <span data-contrast="auto">ATFX </span><span data-contrast="auto">ने</span> <span data-contrast="auto">पारदर्शिता</span> <span data-contrast="auto">पर</span> <span data-contrast="auto">ध्यान</span> <span data-contrast="auto">देने</span> <span data-contrast="auto">और</span> <span data-contrast="auto">प्लेटफ़ॉर्म</span> <span data-contrast="auto">उपलब्</span><span data-co